eu.trentorise.smartcampus.osm.android.views.overlay

Class Overlay

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.trentorise.smartcampus.osm.android.views.overlay.Overlay
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OverlayConstants
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DirectedLocationOverlay, LongPressOverlay, MapEventsOverlay, MyLocationOverlay, PathOverlay, SafeDrawOverlay, SimpleLocationOverlay

    public abstract class Overlay
extends java.lang.Object
implements OverlayConstants
    Base class representing an overlay which may be displayed on top of a MapView. To add an overlay, subclass this class, create an instance, and add it to the list obtained from getOverlays() of MapView. This class implements a form of Gesture Handling similar to android.view.GestureDetector.SimpleOnGestureListener and GestureDetector.OnGestureListener. The difference is there is an additional argument for the item.
    Author:
    Nicolas Gramlich
